Package: smurfs
Title: Sampling Multivariate Uniform Records with Fixed Sum
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Weinstock", "Aaron", email="aaron.weinstock@nltgis.com", role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: R implementations of algorithms for the generation of unbiased task 
    utilization vectors. A task utilization vector defines the utilization of a
    set of n tasks with a fixed total utilization. The total utilization, as 
    well as the range possible utilization values for each task, may vary case 
    by case.
